parameters: \n<Robert Edward Jr.>I'm right at home on this throne!
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>Oh, it's just a chair?
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>This castle is very large. I'm amazed that
it hasn't collapsed over the past millenium.
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>I suppose the Last Stand must have cast some
sort of enchantment along with the seal in order
to keep the castle's structural integrity.
\n<Roberta Edward>You were... brave. When you opened the seal.
